headline: DAT Names Jana Galbraith as Chief People Officer
summary: BEAVERTON, Ore., March 03, 2025--DAT Freight & Analytics today announced the appointment of Jana Galbraith as Chief People Officer (CPO). Galbraith will lead DAT’s people strategy, talent development, and organizational culture initiatives, ensuring the company attracts, retains, and empowers top talent to further drive innovation and growth.
